AD_TAB.NAME: Withholding
AD_TAB.HELP: The Withholding Tab defines any withholding information for this business partner.

AD_TAB.NAME: Customer
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define customer properties of a business partner that will purchase items from you.
AD_TAB.HELP: Customer related data can be entered and configured once the "Customer" check-box is enabled.

AD_TAB.NAME: Customer List
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create a business partner to be used in the application.
AD_TAB.HELP: There are many business partner types such as customers, suppliers and employees you can define and configure.

AD_TAB.NAME: Basic Discount
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Add Basic Discounts which may be made available to this business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Basic Discount tab allows you to add and configure business partner Basic Discounts.

AD_TAB.NAME: Employee Accounting
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create and edit G/L accounts to be used in transactions including a selected employee.
AD_TAB.HELP: The ledger accounts to be used while posting employee related transactions such as paryroll accounting could be added in this tab.

AD_TAB.NAME: Shipment Route
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create a delivery position for this business partner on a defined shipment route, in case the wharehouse is defined as Shipment Vehicle.
AD_TAB.HELP: Create a delivery position for this business partner on a defined shipment route, in case the wharehouse is defined as Shipment Vehicle.

AD_TAB.NAME: Contact
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define contacts for dealing with a selected business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Contact tab allows you to add and configure the business partner contacts you deal with.

AD_TAB.NAME: Location/Address
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define locations or addresses for the business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Business partner locations and full address details can be set up in this tab.

AD_TAB.NAME: Bank Account
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define bank accounts to be used for monetary transactions with this business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Bank account tab allows you to list and setup business partner bank accounts.

AD_TAB.NAME: Employee
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define employee properties of a business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: A business partner can be set up as employee once the check-box "Employee" is enabled.

AD_TAB.NAME: Customer Accounting
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create and edit G/L accounts to be used in transactions including a selected customer.
AD_TAB.HELP: Customer accounting tab allows you to configure the ledger accounts to be used while posting customer related transactions such as customer receivables and customer advances to the general ledger.

AD_TAB.NAME: Vendor Accounting
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create and edit G/L accounts to be used in transactions including a selected vendor.
AD_TAB.HELP: Vendor accounting tab allows you to configure the ledger accounts to be used while posting vendor related transactions such as vendor liabilities and vendor advanced payments to the general ledger.

AD_TAB.NAME: Volume Discount Settlement
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: View invoices for volume discounts accepted and used by this business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: View invoices for volume discounts accepted and used by this business partner.

AD_TAB.NAME: Volume Discount
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Add volume discounts which may be made available to this business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Add volume discounts which may be made available to this business partner.

AD_TAB.NAME: Product Template
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create a product template to be used to carry out simple sales order transactions with this business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Create a product template to be used to carry out simple sales order transactions with this business partner.

AD_TAB.NAME: Vendor/Creditor
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define a business partner as a vendor who will sell items.
AD_TAB.HELP: Vendor or Creditor related data can be entered and configured once the "Vendor" check-box is enabled.
